
	bc - brainfuck compiler for amd64 plus transpiler for amd64 and aarch64

	this is my first compiler. For the first time i feel myself like a real programmer
	:)

	$ make
	$ ./bc --usage
	$ ./bc -c brainfuck/e.bf
	$ chmod +x a.out
	$ ./a.out

	notes:
	bc only produces ELF files for amd64 arch, however it can produce arm64 if you provide
	the --source (-S) flag and -A arm64 (--arch=arm64)

